### ============================================================
### ADMIN REGISTRATIONS API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@adminEmail = admin@kompeta.test
@adminPassword = admin12345
@targetRegistrationId = 1

### ============================================================
### 1. LOGIN ADMIN
### ============================================================
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin",
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

### ============================================================
### 2. LIST REGISTRASI PENDING (default)
### ============================================================
# @name pendingRegistrations
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 3. LIST REGISTRASI DENGAN FILTER
### ============================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations?status=pending&role=mitra&mitra_type=perusahaan&per_page=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 4. DETAIL REGISTRASI
###    Gunakan id dari response pendingRegistrations
### ============================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations/{{targetRegistrationId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 5. APPROVE REGISTRASI
### ============================================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations/{{targetRegistrationId}}/approve
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 6. REJECT REGISTRASI
### ============================================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations/{{targetRegistrationId}}/reject
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 7. AKSES TANPA TOKEN (harus 401)
### ============================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 8. AKSES DENGAN TOKEN NON-ADMIN (harus 403)
###    Contoh gunakan token sekolah/mitra dari auth.http
### ============================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/registrations
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer GANTI_DENGAN_TOKEN_NON_ADMIN

###
